  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Capacity development for workers&#x2019; organizations; mainstreaming tripartism in the Sida Programme</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will be implemented by ACTRAV with the following aims: strengthening the capacities of trade union organizations covering the broad area of Decent Work.; mainstreaming workers&#x2019; participation in the overall SIDA programme. In particular the ACTRAV&#x2019;s project will focus on three strategic areas of work, namely: -Freedom of association and the process of strengthening workers&#x2019; organizations in the exporting processing zones (EPZ). -Develop the advanced knowledge and research capacity of workers&#x2019; organizations in the area of Job-inclusive growth and working conditions. -Develop advanced knowledge and labour education in the area of OSH.</narrative>
  </description>
